  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pup Champs</strong> is a cozy tactical puzzle game from the makers of Railbound and inbento. Use your wits to become a coach, guide a team of adorable pups and solve over 170 hand-crafted challenges!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848800/extras/86f9748735b153fac735ec30899ce329.avif?t=1762941517\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLAN YOUR ACTIONS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Position your players just right, clear their passing lanes, avoid hazards, outsmart the opponents and lead the pups to victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848800/extras/21e2492b773098e8c29d6ac8be34a37f.poster.avif?t=1762941517\" width=600 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848800/extras/21e2492b773098e8c29d6ac8be34a37f.webm?t=1762941517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848800/extras/21e2492b773098e8c29d6ac8be34a37f.mp4?t=1762941517\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BECOME A PUZZLE CHAMPION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each chapter brings in unexpected challenges - balls get stuck in the mud, monkeys mimic your movements, bunnies react to passes, and more! Where some players see an obstacle, a skilled coach can spot an opportunity...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848800/extras/e32967ad374c7c137841a199de2a159d.avif?t=1762941517\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A STORY ABOUT BONDS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In between solving puzzles discover a tale of friendship and sports told through interactive motion comics. As a retired soccer coach use your experience and wits to help out a bunch of clumsy pups come together and form a great team!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848800/extras/2e10d87c140f5bf12d83e5e1d3809a6b.poster.avif?t=1762941517\" width=600 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848800/extras/2e10d87c140f5bf12d83e5e1d3809a6b.webm?t=1762941517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848800/extras/2e10d87c140f5bf12d83e5e1d3809a6b.mp4?t=1762941517\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FOR PUZZLE NOVICES AND EXPERTS ALIKE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We designed Pup Champs to be accessible to everyone. A series of carefully crafted puzzles will guide you to shine on the field and score game-winning goals. Want an additional challenge? We've got plenty of bonus levels to satisfy you!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pup Champs</strong> is a cozy tactical puzzle game from the makers of Railbound and inbento. Use your wits to become a coach, guide a team of adorable pups and solve over 170 hand-crafted challenges!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848800/extras/86f9748735b153fac735ec30899ce329.avif?t=1762941517\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLAN YOUR ACTIONS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Position your players just right, clear their passing lanes, avoid hazards, outsmart the opponents and lead the pups to victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848800/extras/21e2492b773098e8c29d6ac8be34a37f.poster.avif?t=1762941517\" width=600 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848800/extras/21e2492b773098e8c29d6ac8be34a37f.webm?t=1762941517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848800/extras/21e2492b773098e8c29d6ac8be34a37f.mp4?t=1762941517\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BECOME A PUZZLE CHAMPION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each chapter brings in unexpected challenges - balls get stuck in the mud, monkeys mimic your movements, bunnies react to passes, and more! Where some players see an obstacle, a skilled coach can spot an opportunity...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848800/extras/e32967ad374c7c137841a199de2a159d.avif?t=1762941517\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A STORY ABOUT BONDS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In between solving puzzles discover a tale of friendship and sports told through interactive motion comics. As a retired soccer coach use your experience and wits to help out a bunch of clumsy pups come together and form a great team!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848800/extras/2e10d87c140f5bf12d83e5e1d3809a6b.poster.avif?t=1762941517\" width=600 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848800/extras/2e10d87c140f5bf12d83e5e1d3809a6b.webm?t=1762941517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848800/extras/2e10d87c140f5bf12d83e5e1d3809a6b.mp4?t=1762941517\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FOR PUZZLE NOVICES AND EXPERTS ALIKE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We designed Pup Champs to be accessible to everyone. A series of carefully crafted puzzles will guide you to shine on the field and score game-winning goals. Want an additional challenge? We've got plenty of bonus levels to satisfy you!</p>",
